{
  "stem": "21308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I used to go to chapel on my own.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I used to go with a Welshman, and he was a chapel man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we used to go to the local chapel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were allowed to walk there on her own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then when we'd finished, we used to have to get a hold of the minister and he would sign the ticket for us to prove we'd been.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If he didn't, then we got in hot water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it would be July of '34.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we caught the train and we went up to Edinburgh to join our regiment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the very lowest gunner-- gunner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, it's a private in the infantry, trooper the Calvary, trooper the Armored Corps, gunner in the Artillery.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's not a facetious answer, Christian, but he does as he's told.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if he doesn't, he's in the shit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you got opportunities to get on, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once you got into a service unit, you had an opportunity to train for various things like-- which required high grade maths and that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You did signaling, we learned to-- most of our equipment was World War I signaling equipment then.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you learned to ride and do various things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the thing that-- again, it's with afterthought-- when we were in Edinburgh, we never worked with the infantry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, that's significant because we were field gunners but nobody ever thought of [? mixing ?] the two together and training together, inter-service training.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We never worked with the Navy, we never worked with Royal Air Force.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
